details.name: Kolkata Subhas Chandra Bose International Airport

comment.content:
The pros: Lots of food to eat, lots to shop, entry with the help of Digiyatra (a Government of India app) was super smooth. 

The cons: Dirty loos especially near Gates 14-17. 

Wifi sucks.
